high_descs: Walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the counter and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the upper cabinet to the right of the microwave and take out the grey plate, then close the cabinet.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right and look up at the microwave.
Put the grey plate in the microwave and close the door, turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds take the now heated grey plate out and close the microwave.
Turn right and walk towards the counter, then hang a right and walk up to the fridge.
Put the heated grey plate in the fridge and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated grey plate in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk ahead and veer right to the stove.
Take the plate out of the cabinet to the right of the microwave.
Heat the plate in the oven.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the plate in the fridge on the shelf with the lettuce and egg on it, to the left of both items.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated plate in a fridge.

high_descs: Open cupboard on the right of microwave, get the plate
Move to the front of the microwave
Put the plate in the microwave, close door, retrieve the plate from the microwave
Turn around and walk to the fridge
Put the plate on the top shelf of the fridge
anns.task_desc: Retrieve plate from cupboard, insert it into microwave, take the plate to the fridge
